thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by John Brennan

author: John Brennan
title: John Brennan
text: I came into the Brisbane store to try different studio mixing headphones. In the end, took their advice and settled for a pair that were perfect for the style of production I do and cost less than the other pair I had in mind. There's still some honest people out there. Thanks Store DJ
